==English==
===Etymology===
From {{L.}} [[calcarius]], derived from {{L.}} [[calx]] meaning "lime."  Similar to [[calcium]].

===Adjective===
'''calcareous'''
# resembling or containing [[calcium carbonate]] or [[limestone]];  [[chalky]]

